OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FA Conservative peer and former
OL,7,FScottish Secretary has urged Labour
OL,8,Fnot to oust Sir Keir Starmer because
OL,9,Fchanging prime minister for the sixth
OL,10,Ftime in 10 years would be "damaging to
OL,11,Fthe country".
OL,13,FLord Jack of Courance was "in the
OL,14,Fbunker and was very loyal" to Boris
OL,15,FJohnson when he was forced out by
OL,16,Fcabinet resignations as his
OL,17,Fadministration was dogged by a series
OL,18,Fof scandals, including partygate.
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@LO]uD@[OUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
