CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FHe then served under Liz Truss and
OL,7,FRishi Sunak being one of only two
OL,8,Fcabinet secretaries to remain in post
OL,9,Fthroughout each of the last three Tory
OL,10,Fpremierships.
OL,12,FLord Jack said there are
OL,13,F"similarities" between the final weeks
OL,14,Fof Mr Johnson's time in Downing Street
OL,15,Fwith the pressure being put on Sir
OL,16,FKeir by his own MPs.
OL,18,F"I'm not saying it's triggering me but
OL,19,FI'm seeing it all again," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]zD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
