PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FHe still believes that Mr Johnson
OL,7,Fshould not have quit in the wake of
OL,8,Fmore than 50 resignations from his
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FFormer Dumfries and Galloway MP Lord
OL,12,FJack said Labour should "keep calm and
OL,13,Fcarry on" and not force Sir Keir out
OL,14,Fof office.
OL,16,F"They should stick with the prime
OL,17,Fminister who got them a huge
OL,18,Fmajority," he said.
OL,26,@tD@YOUuD@IO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
