PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,F"They should recognise that it's
OL,7,Fmidterm. Mrs Thatcher had bad
OL,8,Fmidterms. Tony Blair had bad midterms.
OL,10,F"But you have to stick with the
OL,11,Fmanifesto, stick with the prime
OL,12,Fminister and hold your nerve."
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,15,Fis running in next month's Makerfield
OL,16,Fbyelection and has vowed to "change
OL,17,FLabour" and improve the lives of
OL,18,Fvoters if elected.
OL,20,FHe is widely expected to run for his
OL,21,Fparty's leadership if he becomes an MP.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@^O]
