OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FWes Streeting last week quit as Health
OL,7,FSecretary and has confirmed he will
OL,8,Fstand in any race to replace the Prime
OL,9,FMinister, who has indicated he would
OL,10,Ffight any challenge.
OL,12,FA clutch of ministers and ministerial
OL,13,Faides who are seen as loyal to Mr
OL,14,FStreeting have also quit their jobs in
OL,15,Frecent weeks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
