PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FLord Jack said he thought some of Sir
OL,7,FKeir's critics from the 2024 general
OL,8,Felection intake "didn't expect to be
OL,9,FMPs, aren't immersed in politics,
OL,10,Fprobably live most of their lives
OL,11,Fonline and are, I suspect, panicking a
OL,12,Fbit about where Labour are in the
OL,13,Fpolls".
OL,15,FHe said they should "stay calm, hold
OL,16,Fyour nerve and stick with the prime
OL,17,Fminister you've got".
OL,26,@pD@QOUuD@FO]wD@UOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
