PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FLord Jack added: "He got you a big
OL,7,Fmajority. Just to dump prime ministers
OL,8,Fmid-term because you don't like where
OL,9,Fthey are sitting in the opinion polls
OL,10,Fwhen they are actually following
OL,11,Fthrough on their manifesto that
OL,12,Feveryone was elected on is a very
OL,13,Fstrange way to behave.
OL,15,F"And it's actually very unsettling for
OL,16,Fthe United Kingdom. We've had too many
OL,17,Fprime ministers in too short a period
OL,18,Fof time. We need to have some
OL,19,Fstability."
OL,26,@nD@ROUwD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
