CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1779459070
OL,3,CUnlikely allies: Conservative peer
OL,4,Csays Labour should 'stick with' Starmer
OL,6,FHe said the regular turnover in No10
OL,7,Fwas "damaging to the country" and said
OL,8,Fthat had cost the government through
OL,9,Fan increase in the cost of borrowing
OL,10,Fmoney for public spending.
OL,12,FThe UK has changed prime ministers
OL,13,Ffive times since the 2016 EU
OL,14,Freferendum.
OL,16,FTheresa May replaced David Cameron in
OL,17,Fthe wake of the Leave vote, before she
OL,18,Fwas succeeded by Mr Johnson.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@]O]
